This add-on is quick to install and completely hassle free. There are no preferences or settings. Just install and go. 
After the installation, when you visit a Twitter profile, look for the ClickableNow icon in your Firefox status bar. If you see the icon, pass your mouse over links on the background image. 
Make Your Twitter Background Clickable 
Visit http://ClickableNow.com. 
Support
Support for this add-on is provided by the developer at http://clickablenow.com/support.htm or by sending an e-mail to support at clickablenow dot com